<h2>What a Redesign Actually Involves</h2>
<p>A proper website redesign isn't just a fresh coat of paint. At Tupate Studio, a redesign involves:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Audit of your existing site</strong>, We identify what's working, what's broken, and what SEO equity to preserve.</li>
  <li><strong>New information architecture</strong>, We restructure your pages for better user flow and conversion.</li>
  <li><strong>New custom design</strong>, Built from scratch to match your current brand and goals.</li>
  <li><strong>Performance rebuild</strong>, Hand-coded for speed, not loaded with plugins.</li>
  <li><strong>SEO migration</strong>, Old URLs are redirected, meta tags updated, and rankings protected.</li>
</ul>

